      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe the condition of this beauty\u2014it's absolute perfection. It\u2019s been tucked away in a garage and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch, the interior is spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. I've babied this car since day one, but it's finally time for someone else to enjoy it. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
