    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, featuring the legendary S54 straight-six engine with its factory-spec individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous throttle response. The powertrain is mated to a crisp ZF 6-speed manual gearbox, ensuring mechanical purity. This unit has undergone a comprehensive technical refresh, including a bulletproofed VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its original geometry with bushings in flawless condition, providing the precise feedback and damping characteristics expected of a showroom-quality M-car. Every mechanical component, from the variable M differential lock to the high-pressure braking system, operates with surgical precision.",
      "price": 48500.0,
