    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional specimen in pristine, showroom condition. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating and zero imperfections\u2014no chips, no scratches, and no swirls. The original alloy wheels are flawless, with no curb rash or pitting. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the factory scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is perfect, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio exclusively from authorized dealerships. With remarkably low mileage and a history of adult-only ownership, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives like new. The sale includes both original keys, all factory manuals, and a custom-fit indoor car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
